column12:
Nice clean rooms and well presented common areas;
Good restaurant;
Friendly and competent staff;
Nice well equipped gym;
Impressive pool;
Beach across the road and garden / lawn area backs directly onto lagoon

We understood the facility was to shortly close for refurbishment

Airport - 20 min
Colombo - 60 min
Negombo - 15 min tuk-tuk

On the one hand, this hotel is a bit out of the way and isolated;  you cant really walk anywhere other than the property next door. On the other hand, Negombo town is a bit built up and chaotic and tuk-tuks are easy to find and cheap and on balance this is a good location.

